Installation
============

Getting up and running
----------------------

Install the Haskell interpreter GHCI:

    http://www.haskell.org/platform/

Install the Haskell dependency management system cabal:

    http://www.haskell.org/cabal/

    (you will need to follow further instrucions)

Install tutorial dependencies:

    cabal update
    cabal install QuickCheck
    cabal install test-framework-quickcheck2
    cabal install test-framework-hunit

Type 'ghci' from the top level of this project.  This loads
the .ghci file which references src/Course.hs

You're off and running :-)
